Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我得尊称你为"大人" 那我就放弃计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If I have to call you "Sir," I am going to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去和那个可能会在我睡着时吃掉我的眼睛的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and live in a ghost town with a mad magician woman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发疯的女魔法师住在鬼城里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}who will probably eat my eyes while I sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能独居得太久了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I may have been on my own too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止破坏 停止放火\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No more destruction. No more fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀光所有人 但要保住这座城\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Kill the people, but leave the city standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传令下去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Tell the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许将来会有其他人占领这座城\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Perhaps others will occupy this city one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又或者 它会变成一处古迹\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Or, perhaps, it will become a monument.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又一个死在睡梦中的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Another hopeful idea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,满怀希望的想法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}that died in its sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多美好的夜晚啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's a beautiful night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么鬼东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可能就是真正的地狱\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, that is, very probably, actually, Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And how would you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和波西米亚国王相处过一个可怕的夜晚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}One terrible night with the King of Bohemia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还吸食了一袋不是鸦片的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and a bag of something that turned out not to be opium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的来不及讲故事了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We really don't have time for the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能关上通往地狱的门吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Can you close that door into Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不容易\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, not easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我愿意试试\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But, I will try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛珐 你会力挺我吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sypha, do you have my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这东西怎么还不死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}How is this thing still standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为它聚集着最近被杀的人的灵魂\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because it's been filled with the souls of the recently murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要多杀几次才行吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So, I'm going to have to kill it several times over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还说村里的晚上没什么消遣\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And they say there's nothing fun to do in villages at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉 你这个混蛋\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sala, you fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动作很快啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你击败我了 好样的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You have bested me. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你可能赢不了这场仗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But you may not win the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是我的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}My men are everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sala.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你穿过后方的空地进入树林\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Take the back field into the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在小路的岔路口向右走 越过小河 直到看见一棵苹果树\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Go right at the fork and over the creek until you reach the apple tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在那棵树前\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Stand in front of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就会看到安全之路\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You will see your path to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么告诉我这个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why? Why would you tell me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到头来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It turns out that you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的判断力比我更好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}were the better judge of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 萨拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Run, Sala!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我撑不住了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can't get hold of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这该死的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是为了复活该死的弗拉德·特佩斯吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All this to bring back Vlad bloody Tepes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的死亡和恐怖都是为了那个吸血鬼吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All this death and horror for that leech?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这一切\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes. All this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们屠杀整个镇子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All the strength you gathered
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸食他们的灵魂 就是为了聚集力量\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}from murdering a town and drinking its soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能移动回廊里的窗口\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can't move the window in the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你能\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But, you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现出我想看的东西 你这该死的杂种\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Show me what I want to see, you fucking bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他果然是魔法师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He really is a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔蒙特 杀了它\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Belmont! Kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要关闭回廊了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm closing the Corridor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Get out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们两位\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Thank you both!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'll see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在骗我们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You've been lying to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为所有人都欺骗我们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because everybody lies to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都对我们有所隐瞒\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Everybody hides things from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会帮我们的 因为没人会帮我们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You won't help us. Because nobody helps us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会搞清楚怎么移动这座城堡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We will work out how to move this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会弄清你所有的秘密\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We will find all your secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后用它们建造自己的帝国\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We will use them to build our own empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把一切都给了你们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I gave you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 才没有 没人会那么做\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No, you didn't. Nobody does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半个世界的人都在欺骗我们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We have been lied to and cheated across half the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你指望我们会相信你不一样吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you expect us to believe you're different?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我尽力了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I tried to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还没教我们魔法 你不会移动城堡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You haven't taught us magic. You won't move the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和其他人没什么两样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're just like all the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 我知道你们吃尽了苦头\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Please. I know your lives have been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但并非全世界都与你们为敌\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But the world is not against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不与你们为敌\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am not against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当然不是了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Of course you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你已经死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉过你们 我父亲不喜欢魔法武器\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I told you my father didn't like magical weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我没说我没用过它们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I did not say I didn't use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没骗过你们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I never lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了萨拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've killed Sala.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你穿过后方的空地进入树林\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Take the back field into the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在小路的岔路口向右走\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Go right at the fork in the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会找到他\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我的刀给我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Find me my knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:15:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我要在地狱等那个混蛋\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because, I'm going to wait for that bastard in hell
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他来了 我要再杀他一次\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and kill him all over again when he arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烧掉我的房子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Burn my house down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他身下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's all that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是些什么啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}under him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这陷阱使用得很频繁\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This thing's been used a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些小骨头是什么的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What are those small bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动物吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他让我烧掉房子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He asked me to burn it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房子还撑得住呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's actually still standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该不该烧掉仅存的房屋之一呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Should we burn down one of the few buildings left?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是他的临终遗愿\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was his last request.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进去看看吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想知道那扇门后面是什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I just want to know what's behind that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不太对\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That doesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 这家伙做事井井有条\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Come on. This guy was so organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面也许有一些幸存者能用上的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There may be something the survivors could really use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的每个小故事都影响巨大\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Here, every little story is a huge thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,农牧事故 疾病\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A farming accident. A sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷路的孩子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A lost child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得不说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听上去管理小镇可一点也好玩\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}running a town does not sound like it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中自有它的小乐趣\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It has its little pleasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坑里的衣服碎片\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The scraps of clothing in the pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小骨头\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The small bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说是他杀了萨拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He said he killed Sala.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是他挖的坑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was his pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是法官\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He was the Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他找到了自己的小乐趣\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And he found his little pleasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想离开这里 现在就走\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I want to leave here, now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不回来了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉娜是个天才\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Morana's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那都是我的主意\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was all my idea, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我...  -别说了 斯崔格\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- I... - Leave it, Striga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说一遍 莫拉娜是个天才\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Say it. Morana's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的主意\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was still my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的主意相当于\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Your idea was the equivalent
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个村野白痴走进来说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}of the village idiot walking in here and saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"我觉得我们可以通过揍一条鱼来点火"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}"I think we should be able to light fires by punching a fish."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本说不通 而莫拉娜还是做到了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It basically made no sense and Morana made it work anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}For God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯崔格 她知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Striga, she knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然不知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I certainly do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可能知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}How could you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是天才\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都是天才 别争了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're all brilliant. Stop bickering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他来这里干什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丽诺尔 这是我们的房间\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Lenore, this is our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连守卫都不能进来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We don't even let the guards in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们想让赫克托帮忙 所以\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You wanted Hector's help. So,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫克托偶尔可以与我们同席\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hector gets to sit with us sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里有几位吸血鬼魔法师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, we have a few vampire magicians here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我让其中一位做的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I had one of them make those.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还借了他的书\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I also borrowed that book from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个铁匠魔法师 勇敢之选\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The blacksmith magician. Brave choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞期间 斯崔格差点把他放在阳光下暴晒\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Striga almost had him staked out in the sunlight over Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他熔了她的旧盔甲\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}after he melted down her old armor
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想给自己做一双新脚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to make himself new feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他 可爱的老头 不停地抽搐\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's him, lovely old man. Strange twitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是奴隶戒指\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}These are slave rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一个到了赫克托手上\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}One of them found its way on to Hector's hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在他发誓效忠我的时候\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}while he was swearing his loyalty to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 当时他正在我体内\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes. He was inside me at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 你们都知道 赫克托锻造的黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So, as you know, when Hector forges a night creature,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,效忠于他\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}they are loyal to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戒指上的咒语 把他和我绑在了一起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He is bound to me through the spell on these rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当他锻造的黑暗生物时 它们效忠于他\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}When he makes a night creature, they're loyal to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他效忠于我 所以它们也效忠于我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and he swore loyalty to me, so they're loyal to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有这些戒指都是相连的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All these rings are linked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴上戒指 他的黑暗生物也会效忠于你们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Wear the ring, and his night creatures will be loyal to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:22:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果赫克托试图伤害我们 或者摘掉戒指或试图逃跑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And if Hector ever tries to harm us, or take it off, or run away,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的戒指会引发巨痛\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}his ring will cause him so much pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他以为自己的心脏快掉出来了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}that he'll think he shat out his own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题解决了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Problem solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Bloody hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为回报 我们要改造一栋旧楼让他住进去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}In return, we're going to convert one of the old outbuildings for him to live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.58,0:22:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要装饰得好看些\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're going to make it nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.33,0:22:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要和我们活得一样舒服\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He's going to live just as well as we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在城堡里自由通行\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and he's going to have freedom of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看不行\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看行 他总要有所回报\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I do. He gets something back from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会拥有舒适的生活和安全感\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He gets a comfortable life. He gets to feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我能不能…  -莫拉娜会...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- Do I get to... - Morana will...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 大人们在说话\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Shush. The real people are talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉娜会负责安排的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Morana will make the arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯崔格组织锻造\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Striga will organize the forging.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡米拉必须同意这一切并忍气吞声\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla will agree to all this and live with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是天才 她才是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm not a genius. She is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:22:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位吸血鬼姐妹一直都有自己的诡计\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The vampire sister had her own scheme all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.12,0:23:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你收养了他\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You adopted him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.79,0:23:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡米拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 好了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All right. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的住处需要一张很大的床\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And the house will need a really big bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他还是个性爱高手\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It turns out he's actually fairly good at sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想培养他\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and I want to train him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走开 真的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Get away from me. Uck, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.79,0:23:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走开\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Please leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要知道这个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't think I needed that information?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-再见  -我需要知道那个吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- Bye-bye. - Did I need to know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.45,0:23:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你耍了我 把我变成了你的奴隶\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You tricked me and made me your slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I did no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把我变成了奴隶\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You made me a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生结束了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}My life is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.25,0:23:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的命得救了 赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Your life is saved, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给了你一直以来真正需要的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I gave you what you always really needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.75,0:23:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把你变成了我的宠物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I made you into my pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.41,0:24:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是大错特错了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This could not have gone more wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.87,0:24:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.45,0:24:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们花了几个月时间过你的生活\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We've spent a couple of months living your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.91,0:24:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满冒险和胜利\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Adventures and victories.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.79,0:24:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 该过我的生活了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And now, we're living my life.
